### Step 3: Deploy Exporters (Data Sources)

Deploy Node Exporter for system metrics:

```bash
ssh -i {{security.sshKeyPath}} root@$VPS_IP "
  docker run -d \
    --name node-exporter \
    --network appwrite \
    -p {{monitoring.nodeExporterPort}}:9100 \
    --restart unless-stopped \
    -v /proc:/host/proc:ro \
    -v /sys:/host/sys:ro \
    -v /:/rootfs:ro \
    prom/node-exporter:latest \
    --path.procfs=/host/proc \
    --path.sysfs=/host/sys \
    --collector.filesystem.mount-points-exclude='^/(sys|proc|dev|host|etc)(\$|/)'
"
```

